name: Pixel
description: Pixel is bringing gamification to NFTs and Defi. Their first project, PixelPotus.com, is an early collectable on Tezos and has been in the top 5 on DappRadar for months. The Pixel Debates TCG release is quickly approaching and will be the first major utility for the PXL token. This is just the beginning from a proven team with an exciting roadmap.
